cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

The paper proposes a deep convolutional neural network for remote sensing image pan-sharpening, which involves image processing and computer vision techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves the use of feature extraction and fusion techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another possible category. Additionally, the paper involves remote sensing and image processing techniques, which makes cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia) possible categories.
